Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.95,0:00:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最喜歡姐姐大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.77,0:00:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有你們兩個這麼可愛的妹妹 好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.47,0:00:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人 姐姐大人……
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做了一個這樣的夢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個夢一定會成真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.42,0:00:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不 我要讓它成真 用充滿心中那愛的力量！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.42,0:02:24.55,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(420,0)\1c&H3A9EF7&}#03 感受到愛情喜劇的波動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:24.55,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(420,0)\3c&HF2C855&\bord6}#03 感受到愛情喜劇的波動
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇哦 西式早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}起司 濃濃的起司真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.93,0:02:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒這麼誇張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白醬很喜歡麵包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}牛奶和柳橙汁你要哪個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再來一份 還有牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳 我昨晚做了個超級幸福的夢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想聽嗎 想不想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不想 反正不是什麼好夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要這樣說嘛 想讓你聽聽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我變成了身騎白馬的王子殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都說不想聽了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別說了 真白很為難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白在家裡比較蠻橫也很任性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不擅長和不按照自己想法行事的人相處
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這完全不是幫我說好話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.98,0:03:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊呀啊呀 聽到了很好的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.01,0:03:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜呢 這樣的早餐還合胃口嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.62,0:03:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果覺得還是有味噌湯比較好 或者想吃鹹菜 也可以提出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅做的飯菜 無論什麼都好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼情況 這種想吐的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒錯 這就是愛情喜劇的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒 快點吃完去上學
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.28,0:03:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 原來真白醬喜歡吃西餐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且還喜歡西式糕點喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:04:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊對了 明天休息 想做司康餅了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.78,0:04:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司康餅？真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早就想嚐一下了 憧憬已久的司康餅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}情緒高漲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人也很期待的呢
Comment: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 怎麼了嗎真白醬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個……
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給我給我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.21,0:04:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 好忐忑 我不擅長這些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒關係沒關係 放鬆就能做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.32,0:04:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅不喜歡運動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.90,0:04:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為有負擔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.43,0:04:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在看哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.56,0:04:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那是在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.74,0:04:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是手球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜在做守門員呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.13,0:04:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜擅長運動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 也不能說是不擅長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:07.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 總覺得不太好弄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我能理解 高個子沒表情不說話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看不穿他的動向啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然已經同居半個月了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.15,0:05:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但還是不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.20,0:05:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜到底是個什麼樣的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}輪到小紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.41,0:05:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果真不擅長運動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.61,0:05:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然是因為負擔太重了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過還是小心一點好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅人氣還是蠻高的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊 只不過小紅自己沒有察覺罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為都被紅緒掩蓋了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不過紅緒居然能接受白夜是小紅的未婚夫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為是爺爺決定的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 好…好累
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.90,0:06:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}桃內真由良 開始囉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真由良真輕鬆啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 我哥哥除了個高沒有別的優點 還帶了個小姑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.66,0:06:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}突 突然這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.76,0:06:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1248,435)\fad(300,0)\c&H4D2BB1&}\N突\N然\N嚇\N到\N{\i1}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仔細想想的確是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.29,0:06:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為紅緒在身邊不容易察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.71,0:06:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個問題 夜之森同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:07:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅學習又好又會做家務人還很體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.52,0:07:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正確 做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}更重要的是還有那兩個火箭炮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那可是大規模殺傷性武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大胸有加分哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果早上穿著圍裙叫你起床……
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.77,0:07:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給我再加把勁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.69,0:07:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖說小紅是你的未婚妻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但如果她本人不願意而逃走的話 就全完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅很受歡迎的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.75,0:07:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再發呆的話 就會被別人搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 就像那個炸好的吃的突然被老鷹叼走一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}老鷹？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}打個比方而已啦 不是真的叼走啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總之請你振作起來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 贈品？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然已經晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是不能收學生的這種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}稍微打擾一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅 是紅緒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人有什麼事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}今天找深愛的真白有事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}笨蛋來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愛妹妹的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.28,0:08:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}多麼帥氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這些人真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請收下 邀請函哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1253,419)\c&HA55E8C&\fad(300,0)\b1}\N不\N討\N厭\N這\N樣\N的\N演\N出
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.39,0:08:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為紅緒姐對真白醬很關心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以小紅有點寂寞了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.75,0:08:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才…沒有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}邀請函是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}給我我深愛的幼女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白碳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請務必來學生會室喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後來舉辦我計畫的時裝展覽會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.65,0:09:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一臉微笑撕的粉碎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你給我夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.80,0:09:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撫子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}撫子大人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.17,0:09:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉了 請不要在意好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒…沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 有興趣的話請過來玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.52,0:09:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也有點心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 我去 現在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.22,0:09:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我今天要去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哎呀 真遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼 請你們先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我今天要去上課
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.88,0:09:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣的話…回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.88,0:09:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兩個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說點什麼才好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說點啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說點啥 說點啥 說點啥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}原本就不怎麼說話 不說也好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.31,0:10:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去買點司康餅的材料
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.72,0:10:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一個人不行 有危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能讓你拿重的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}過度保護的老爹嗎喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.55,0:10:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是確實不是壞人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只能順其自然了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}奶茶可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.00,0:10:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還有餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.03,0:10:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.01,0:10:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}松鼠？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼纏著要請她喝茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.93,0:11:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在忙碌的職場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}治癒一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.87,0:11:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}接下來果然
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要把小紅也留在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就像夢裡一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}進展順利 進展順利 進展超順利哇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撫子同學 上茶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}自己泡去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}十分鐘？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.88,0:11:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來了大概有八分半呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.65,0:11:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明那麼不願意 有八分半呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有好感度了 成功啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.24,0:11:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是積極呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.18,0:11:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我今天值日來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有誰來過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.85,0:11:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}來了紅緒她家的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒給了她邀請函
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人給邀請函？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.20,0:11:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特地的讓紅緒給了邀請函？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.96,0:12:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒大人 好好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我好羡慕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.08,0:12:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}下次要挑戰15分鐘哦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.85,0:12:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在開始限時大搶購
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要擠到那裡面去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不能讓小紅去冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.75,0:12:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎 沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.08,0:12:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去下個地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.17,0:12:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我去買點別的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}買完的話就去外面等著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直用客人用的也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.19,0:12:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}會喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃燒殆盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.35,0:12:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}兩位好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為去買東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司康餅的材料買回來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.02,0:12:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}司康餅？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直都做那樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到底發生了啥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是我們的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.20,0:13:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為一直用的是客人用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個是真白的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.84,0:13:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喜歡了…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}學生會室怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.36,0:13:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}被請喝茶了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很好喝哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}還給我吃了餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 姐姐大人沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.77,0:13:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.09,0:13:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H7AB4EF&\3c&H726DE2&\shad0\fad(150,150)}{\pos(640,20)}好喝的茶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.63,0:13:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H7AB4EF&\3c&H726DE2&\shad0\fad(150,150)}{\pos(640,20)}撫子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.22,0:13:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H7AB4EF&\3c&H726DE2&\shad0\fad(150,150)}{\pos(640,20)}很香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H7AB4EF&\3c&H726DE2&\shad0\fad(150,150)}{\pos(640,20)}碎巧克力餅乾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H7AB4EF&\3c&H726DE2&\shad0\fad(150,150)}{\pos(640,20)}咬起來很多奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.14,0:13:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒啥的不認識
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這個是白夜的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有點大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.72,0:13:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼都沒有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜 白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅為我們買了碗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.20,0:14:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是很棒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.80,0:14:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很有一家人的味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.80,0:14:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要回禮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}順便要說出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必須要好好道謝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對小紅的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.84,0:14:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}家長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦…話是這麼說……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.13,0:14:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然有些晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.61,0:14:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以後也請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特地送禮真是感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是…贈品？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安 小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.22,0:14:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}得起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.81,0:15:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅的反應太冷淡了完全不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這種破事就不要一大早打電話過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.42,0:15:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小時候小紅就特別喜歡姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一直黏著我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}走到哪都跟著我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}摔倒哭的時候都是叫我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}洗澡 換衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}睡覺都一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.95,0:15:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以你想說點什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}到了現在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}做飯洗衣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}掃除都是小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以你想說點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我炫耀妹妹 有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.07,0:15:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}休息日最煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是受不了和紅緒在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最討厭周日了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}然後
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.48,0:15:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}討厭…周日嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}最討厭了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.08,0:16:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}家裡來信了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身體還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}學習怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也順便適應社會了沒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.28,0:16:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白可以吃黏黏的食物了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我來回信好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}甜甜的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.66,0:16:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經烤好囉 是司康餅哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我馬上去準備點茶 等我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}過來坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白的座椅是我的大腿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}請你別說話 永遠的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好美味哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是小紅做的 當然好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.02,0:17:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼紅緒這麼自豪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼 難道你是故意的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}故意在臉頰上留點果醬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}FLAG?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我可以當成是立FLAG了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.46,0:17:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讓姐姐幫你弄下來好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.58,0:17:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讓姐姐來幫你舔下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.35,0:17:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好美味啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.59,0:17:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果醬也好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.54,0:17:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 白夜也吃了吧 真是少見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.38,0:17:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜啊 不太喜歡甜食
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.53,0:17:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}平時都不吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要是小紅做的就都好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}接下來 要不要晾衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}晾衣服的話我來幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.06,0:18:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}偶爾周日也要休息一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.24,0:18:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是這樣我不得不再晾一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}確實…雖然我確實晾衣服也做不好……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.93,0:18:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 幫忙的話我還是可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.44,0:18:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}呃 這是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.86,0:18:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那個 我們過的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}黏黏的食物最喜歡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.79,0:18:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}納豆是我現在最熱衷的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:38.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}後面居然印的是喵咪圖案！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.49,0:18:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.29,0:18:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我被羞辱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒 也沒什麼不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.54,0:18:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是女孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒沒做什麼不好的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.77,0:18:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當然不可能的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為知道了尺寸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.92,0:18:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以幹勁十足
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:19:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為了不讓你肚子著涼去買更好的內衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.59,0:19:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 白夜沒在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}出門 寄信去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.88,0:19:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我在廚房 沒注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我能把白夜的也吃掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是再這樣大聲的話真白會生氣的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且還看人家的小內內
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅會生氣什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真想不到 好想死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是為了真白碳而看內衣商品目錄的我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人 我想跟你說一下話 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.69,0:19:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你肯原諒我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦？啥東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.52,0:19:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我好開心好開心哦 小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.66,0:19:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}比起一日三餐我更願意跟小紅說話哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}幹嘛這麼誇張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想問點事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事 我的三圍尺寸？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}必殺技？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}前世？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}座右銘？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.50,0:20:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為你總是說不想讓我有男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.18,0:20:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以想問問你為什麼沒反對白夜的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.67,0:20:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}吃醋了？是吃醋了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.85,0:20:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在吃醋哦 好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}不是 只是很正常的提問的說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.66,0:20:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad0\fad(300,0)\pos(116,645)\c&H322C3F&}習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}其實我是想過些陣子跟你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.18,0:20:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以前跟爺爺一起去過白夜家玩的事你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 雖然記得不是特別清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那時候小紅你從懸崖上掉了下來受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是白夜救了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是說 他是你的救命恩人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}而且還是爺爺決定的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然是我覺得是擅自決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是沒辦法啊 沒辦法啊 小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}冷靜冷靜下來 我心中的破壞神
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an7\fs30}所以沒辦法啊而且還是爺爺決定的事雖然是我覺得是擅自決定的但是沒辦法啊 沒辦法啊 小紅冷靜冷靜下來 我心中的破壞神
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an3}快點回過神來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我當時沒在場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們兩個人去山上玩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}在山上的斜坡滑倒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:15.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為想要救小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以白夜跟你一起掉了下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們倆都受了重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜勉強一個人去通知大人才得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明他自己也受了重傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.97,0:21:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小時候見過面的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不記得了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說是以前見過面的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也就是說那個時候的事情也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.84,0:21:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我竟然說不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.73,0:21:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我都做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太差勁了吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ED
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.03,0:23:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐我很幸福哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.61,0:23:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}噫！！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}下一集 她只是個變態而已
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
